      <hedline>
        <hl1>BUS MOVIES</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>BusTV is set to start showing movies and ads aimed at older audiences aboard Coach USA buses that travel from north Jersey to Atlantic City (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Riders taking the bus from North Jersey to Atlantic City are likely to watch a movie -- and some ads -- provided by an Englewood Cliffs company called BusTV. Coach USA, the company's largest bus company, started this month showing the Disney movie ''Diamonds'' on Leisure Line, Gray Line, Red and Tan, Short Line, Community Coach and Suburban buses, all based in North Jersey and all owned by Coach USA. Before the feature, passengers watch a safety video and then ads aimed at older audiences, for the Senokot laxative and the Mr. Mobility electric wheelchair, for example.</p>
      </block>
